# --- OS / Editor ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# VS Code（如你希望提交团队配置，可删掉这一段或按需改白名单）
.vscode/*
!.vscode/settings.json
!.vscode/extensions.json

# --- Logs ---
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*

# --- Dependencies ---
**/node_modules/

# --- Build outputs ---
**/dist/
**/build/
**/out/
**/.output/

# Vite / Vue / bundler caches
**/.vite/
**/.cache/
**/.temp/

# --- TypeScript caches ---
*.tsbuildinfo

# --- Test / Coverage ---
**/coverage/
**/.nyc_output/

# --- Env files (secrets) ---
**/.env
**/.env.*.local
**/.env.local

# 保留示例文件可提交（例如 server/.env.example）
!**/.env.example

# --- Optional: ignore lockfile backups ---
*.bak

# =========================================================
# 如果你“确实”想整个不提交 web/ 和 server/（连源码都不要入库），取消注释：
# /web/
# /server/